    <summary>
      <attribution license="cc4" from="Microsoft" modified="false" />
      <para>Represents the simpleType element for simple content from XML Schema as specified by the <format type="text/html"><a href="">World Wide Web Consortium (W3C)</a></format>. This class defines a simple type. Simple types can specify information and constraints for the value of attributes or elements with text-only content.</para>
